text: Maryna Pestriakova (born 26 January 1972) is a Ukrainian cross-country skier. She competed at the 1998 Winter Olympics and the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Ukraine Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:Cross- country skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:People from Tomsk
